Quickstrike:





Quickstrike heard loud noises in the corridor. His systems went into 
defense and ran towards them. He could smell a few bots and even 
firepower that had resently been fired, despite his poor sense of 
smell. He found the room where the noise was, discovering that a 
scuffle was the focus. He saw the three bots he saw in the bridge 
before, Black Arachnia lying on the floor, and Tarantulas. 

"T?" he said, wide-eyed. He looked around. He walked towards Black 
Arachnia to aid her. "What in tarnation happpened?" he asked, 
watching Tarantulas.
